  77:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rcc_ex.c ****   *         contains the configuration information for the Extended Peripherals
  78:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rcc_ex.c ****   *         clocks(I2S, SAI, LTDC RTC and TIM).
